This is the so called Bitcoin paper originally written by [[Satoshi_Nakamoto]].

You can read the very fundamentals of the Project in the [Englisch Original](http://bitcoin.org/bitcoin.pdf) and several Translations that are available e.g. [via crowdin](http://crowdin.net/project/bitcoin), on [bitcoinblogger.com](http://www.bitcoinblogger.com/) and in the [Forums](https://bitcointalk.org).

